<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Galaxy Digital Systems</title><link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"><style>
body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#020617);
    color: white;
}

header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
}

header h1 {
    color: #38bdf8;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
}

section {
    padding: 50px;
}

.card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

button {
    background: #38bdf8;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

input, textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0;
    border-radius: 5px;
    border: none;
}

footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #020617;
}

</style></head><body><header>
    <h1>Galaxy Digital Systems</h1>
    <p>Grow Smart, Grow Fast 🚀</p>
</header><section>
    <h2>❌ Problem</h2>
    <div class="card">
        Small businesses spend money on ads but don’t get results due to poor strategy, no funnel, and lack of proper system.
    </div>
</section><section>
    <h2>✅ Our Solution</h2>
    <div class="card">
        We provide AI-powered digital marketing with proper funnel system, automation, and targeted ads to convert leads into customers.
    </div>
</section><section>
    <h2>🎯 Who We Support</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <ul>
            <li>Clothing Shops</li>
            <li>Mobile Shops</li>
            <li>Gyms</li>
            <li>Coaching Classes</li>
            <li>Local Businesses & Startups</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section><section>
    <h2>💼 Our Services</h2><div class="card">
    <h3>AI Marketing</h3>
    <p>We use advanced AI tools to analyze customer behavior and create smart marketing campaigns that target the right audience for better results.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>Sales Funnel Creation</h3>
    <p>We build high-converting sales funnels that guide your customers step-by-step from interest to final purchase.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>Social Media Ads</h3>
    <p>We create and manage Facebook & Instagram ads that attract local customers and generate quality leads.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>Content Creation</h3>
    <p>We design engaging posts, reels, and videos in local languages to connect emotionally with your audience.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>WhatsApp Marketing</h3>
    <p>We help you directly reach your customers using WhatsApp campaigns, voice notes, and personalized communication.</p>
</div>

</section><section>
    <h2>📱 Social Media Marketing</h2><div class="card">
    <h3>Marketing Through Social Media</h3>
    <p>We help businesses grow using platforms like Instagram, Facebook, and WhatsApp by creating engaging content and targeted campaigns that attract the right audience.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>Sales Generation</h3>
    <p>Our strategies focus on converting followers into customers through ads, reels, storytelling, and direct engagement techniques.</p>
</div>

<div class="card">
    <h3>Brand Growth</h3>
    <p>We build strong brand presence with consistent posting, local language content, and emotional connection with audience.</p>
</div>

</section><section>
    <h2>📊 Free Audit Plan</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <ul>
            <li>Business Analysis & Current Performance Review</li>
            <li>Social Media & Ad Strategy Check</li>
            <li>Lead Generation Problem Identification</li>
            <li>Custom Growth Strategy Suggestion</li>
            <li>Free Consultation Call</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section><section>
    <h2>📩 Free Audit Form</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <form id="contactForm">
            <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <input type="email" id="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
            <textarea id="message" placeholder="Tell us about your business" required></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Get Free Audit</button>
        </form>
        <p id="formMsg"></p>
    </div>
</section><footer>
    <p>📧 Email: galaxydigital@gmail.com</p>
    <p>📞 Contact: +91 9123456780</p>
    <p>© 2026 Galaxy Digital Systems</p>
</footer><script>
document.getElementById("contactForm").addEventListener("submit", function(e){
    e.preventDefault();

    fetch("https://formspree.io/f/mayvlrva", {
        method: "POST",
        headers: {
            "Content-Type": "application/json"
        },
        body: JSON.stringify({
            name: document.getElementById("name").value,
            email: document.getElementById("email").value,
            message: document.getElementById("message").value
        })
    })
    .then(res => {
        document.getElementById("formMsg").innerText = "Request Sent Successfully 🚀";
    })
    .catch(err => {
        document.getElementById("formMsg").innerText = "Error ❌";
    });
});
</script></body>
</html>
